flowchart TD
    START((Inbound web call)):::entry
    MC{MC captured?}:::decision
    END_NO_MC((NO_MC_PROVIDED)):::declineEnd
    VERIFY[[Verify FMCSA eligibility]]:::tool
    END_FMCSA((FMCSA_DECLINE)):::declineEnd
    IDENTITY[Confirm legal name<br/>capture caller name + role]:::action
    LANE[Capture lane + equipment + pickup window]:::action
    SEARCH[[Find matching loads<br/>narrow down with carrier]]:::tool
    END_NO_MATCH((NO_MATCH)):::declineEnd
    PITCH[Pitch load at loadboard rate]:::action
    REPLY{Carrier response<br/>to pitched rate?}:::decision
    NEGOTIATE[[Negotiate · up to 3 rounds<br/>see negotiation diagram]]:::subprocess
    NEXT_LOAD{More matching loads?}:::decision
    PIVOT[Try next match]:::action
    END_DECLINE((DECLINED_NO_AGREEMENT)):::declineEnd
    TRANSFER[[Transfer to dispatch]]:::tool
    END_BOOKED((BOOKED)):::successEnd
    POSTCALL[Post-call chain<br/>persist · extract · classify · audit]:::postcall
    STORE[(Calls log → Dashboard)]:::data

    START --> MC
    MC -->|refused| END_NO_MC
    MC -->|yes| VERIFY
    VERIFY -->|decline| END_FMCSA
    VERIFY -->|pass| IDENTITY
    IDENTITY --> LANE
    LANE --> SEARCH
    SEARCH -->|no matches| END_NO_MATCH
    SEARCH -->|match| PITCH
    PITCH --> REPLY
    REPLY -->|accept| TRANSFER
    REPLY -->|counter below| NEGOTIATE
    REPLY -->|walks| NEXT_LOAD
    NEGOTIATE -->|deal reached| TRANSFER
    NEGOTIATE -->|stall / walk| NEXT_LOAD
    NEXT_LOAD -->|yes| PIVOT
    PIVOT --> PITCH
    NEXT_LOAD -->|no more matches| END_DECLINE
    TRANSFER --> END_BOOKED

    END_NO_MC --> POSTCALL
    END_FMCSA --> POSTCALL
    END_NO_MATCH --> POSTCALL
    END_DECLINE --> POSTCALL
    END_BOOKED --> POSTCALL
    POSTCALL --> STORE

    classDef entry fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,stroke-width:2px,color:#451a03
    classDef action fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#0c1e3e
    classDef decision fill:#fed7aa,stroke:#c2410c,stroke-width:1.5px,color:#431407
    classDef tool fill:#e9d5ff,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e0b4b
    classDef subprocess fill:#ccfbf1,stroke:#0d9488,stroke-width:3.5px,color:#042f2e
    classDef successEnd fill:#bbf7d0,stroke:#15803d,stroke-width:3px,color:#052e16
    classDef declineEnd fill:#fecaca,stroke:#b91c1c,stroke-width:2px,color:#450a0a
    classDef postcall fill:#fde68a,stroke:#a16207,stroke-width:2px,color:#451a03
    classDef data fill:#c7d2fe,stroke:#4338ca,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e1b4b
